<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="overwhelm-vt">overwhelm <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌəʊvə'welm/    美 /ˌoʊvər'welm/  </p>
<p>[常用于被动语态]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>使不知所措；压倒：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I <strong>was overwhelmed by</strong> all the flowers and letters of support I received.
收到那么多的鲜花和支持信，我激动得不知如何是好。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>overwhelming /ˌəʊvə'welmɪŋ/ adj   </p></div>